DESCRIPTION:Description This luncheon focuses on discussing Kent's major de
	velopment projects\, growth corridors\, and business attraction strategies
	. Attendees will connect with peers\, engage with speakers\, and gain insi
	ghts for business growth\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/
	membership-luncheon-legislative-wrap/18292752/2026-04-02T00\n\nFrom SEAtod
	ay - Food & Drink
